{"tha-ap314:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap314:0.2":"Arakkhadayakavagga ","tha-ap314:0.3":"Bhojanadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap314:1.1":"“Sujato salalatthiva, ","tha-ap314:1.2":"sobhanjanamivuggato; ","tha-ap314:1.3":"Indalatthirivakase, ","tha-ap314:1.4":"virocati sada jino. ","tha-ap314:2.1":"Tassa devatidevassa, ","tha-ap314:2.2":"vessabhussa mahesino; ","tha-ap314:2.3":"Adasi bhojanamaham, ","tha-ap314:2.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","tha-ap314:3.1":"Tam me buddho anumodi, ","tha-ap314:3.2":"sayambhu aparajito; ","tha-ap314:3.3":"Bhave nibbattamanamhi, ","tha-ap314:3.4":"phalam nibbattatu tava. ","tha-ap314:4.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap314:4.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap314:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap314:4.4":"bhojanassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap314:5.1":"Pancavise ito kappe, ","tha-ap314:5.2":"eko asim amittako; ","tha-ap314:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap314:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap314:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap314:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap314:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap314:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma bhojanadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap314:8.1":"Bhojanadayakattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}